      What is Science at Home? || Sample activity || List of activities
                         included in Science at Home
     __________________________________________________________________

   Science at Home was funded by the US Department of Energy and developed
      by the Science Education Team at Los Alamos National Laboratory.
     __________________________________________________________________

       The physical science activity book is made available through an
           industrial partnership with Curriculum Associates, Inc.

                                  [SAH.GIF]

                                 Awards won!

   Science at Home was created to give students, parents and teachers the
     opportunity to explore and discover science using common, household
                                 materials.
     __________________________________________________________________

   Science at Home is currently available in the United States and Europe.

                             ISBN 0-7609-0236-4

                          To order, call Toll Free,

                               (800) 225-0248

                      or contact your local bookstore.
     __________________________________________________________________

   If you have questions about Science at Home, please Email The Education
                    Program Office or call 505-667-1919.
